title.narrative: Support to IGIF (Indonesia Green Investment Fund)

description.narrative: This activity (Support to IGIF (Indonesia Green Investment Fund)) is a component of Indonesia Low Carbon Growth Project reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,734,922. This component benefits Indonesia, and works in the following sector(s): Environmental policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office, Overseas Development Institute. The start date is 05-07-2010 and the end date is 31-01-2013.
